Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:38.77,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}去实现于天空彼方的约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.91,0:22:46.40,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我祈愿与你并肩前行
Comment: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:48.51,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Beautiful it’s beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.92,0:22:53.21,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}正确与否
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.21,0:22:55.56,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}只取决于自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.78,0:23:03.43,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}时而莫衷一是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:10.34,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}时而词不达意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.34,0:23:12.40,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}这也无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.40,0:23:15.86,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}让弱小的我变得强大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.86,0:23:21.41,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}是为与你相称
Comment: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:25.89,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I ain’t fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:27.89,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我难以割舍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:32.38,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}亦如无法放弃
